* location ^short = "Where the Cryopreservation happened"


//++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++
Profile:  ProcedureOtherTreatmentPcsp
Parent:   Procedure
Id:       Procedure-treatment-otherinfos-eu-pcsp
